the bathroom.

15:09.926 --> 15:12.427
No, no,
that's my place.

15:12.429 --> 15:14.429
Oh, you's locked up.
No, no.

15:14.431 --> 15:18.099
See, I've adopted
a minimalist lifestyle.

15:18.101 --> 15:19.901
That's what you call it?
Yeah, yeah.

15:19.903 --> 15:23.438
I just don't assign meaning
to money or things, you know?

15:23.440 --> 15:25.973
I just, uh, keep myself
in peak condition,

15:25.975 --> 15:27.608
so I'm ready
for adventure.

15:27.610 --> 15:30.545
You know, the elation,
jumping out of an airplane.

15:30.547 --> 15:33.581
Or -- Or the ecstasy of --
of the conquest of reaching

15:33.583 --> 15:36.451
the very top of the snow peaks
of Mount Kilimanjaro.

15:36.453 --> 15:39.120
Or -- Or the thrill
of swimming with the sharks

15:39.122 --> 15:40.354
in South Africa.

15:40.356 --> 15:41.622
You know, these --

15:41.624 --> 15:44.325
these are the things
that I live for.

15:44.327 --> 15:46.494
