15:54.738 --> 15:56.037
I knew it.

15:56.039 --> 15:58.473
Yep,
just like I thought.

15:58.475 --> 16:00.775
You got a crack, but it ain't
leaking through yet.

16:00.777 --> 16:03.144
I'm going to run to the store
and get some supplies.

16:03.146 --> 16:04.779
