16:09.352 --> 16:10.685
I'm having
a little get-together.
Yeah?

16:10.687 --> 16:12.320
Okay, yeah, I got
this fine chick coming to.

16:12.322 --> 16:14.722
She got a glass leg
with Kool-Aid in it.

16:14.724 --> 16:15.990
