16:51.795 --> 16:53.027
Keep going.

16:53.029 --> 16:56.664
You were the one that told him
to show her those moves.

16:56.666 --> 16:58.866
I know what I said!
I was there when I said it.

16:58.868 --> 17:00.702
Give me this.

17:04.450 --> 17:05.883
Sorry to barge in
on you guys.

17:05.885 --> 17:07.351
So, we noticed that Tray
just left your apartment,

17:07.353 --> 17:08.552
