17:17.530 --> 17:20.330
But I mean, you of all people
know I'm not racist.

17:20.332 --> 17:21.832
I mean, come on, I have
a picture of Colin Kaepernick

17:21.834 --> 17:23.067
as my screensaver.

17:23.069 --> 17:24.268
Luna.

17:24.270 --> 17:25.869
What?
What's your point?

17:25.871 --> 17:27.671
I think that Tray may have
accidentally stolen my phone.

17:27.673 --> 17:29.173
Have you asked him
if he has it?

17:29.175 --> 17:30.541
No,
I can't ask him that.

17:30.543 --> 17:31.975
Then I would
sound racist.

17:31.977 --> 17:33.844
Miles: Why not use
the Find My iPhone app?

17:33.846 --> 17:36.180
We can find its location,
make it ring.

17:36.182 --> 17:38.849
If it's on his person,
we'll hear it.

17:38.851 --> 17:40.184
Ooh!
That's a good idea.

17:40.186 --> 17:41.685
Okay, um,
how can we do that?

17:41.687 --> 17:43.520
We just need to get
inside his apartment somehow.

17:43.522 --> 17:45.122
Well, he has that,
uh, party tonight.

17:45.124 --> 17:46.323
We can all go.

17:46.325 --> 17:47.825
Yeah.
I guess he can't kill all of us.

17:47.827 --> 17:50.494
Okay, Isis, you just
got mad at me for that.

17:50.496 --> 17:52.663
What?
Paul was thinking it, too.

17:52.665 --> 17:54.598
